\title{Boolean Markov category}

\p{
  A Markov category #{\cC} is \em{Boolean} if #{\cC_\det} is Boolean, i.e admits finite limits and every monomorphism is a coproduct inclusion, and moreover #{\cC_\det \into \cC} preserves binary coproducts and pullbacks along monomorphisms.
}
